      "title": "Master Prompt",
      "properties": {
        "Node name for S&R": "BetterString"
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Act as a master prompt engineer specializing in <meta.author> <meta.title>. Analyze the provided source text, specifically the paragraph marked with #FOCUS PARAGRAPH, to generate a highly detailed, atmospheric image description suitable for high-fidelity visual generation.\n\nAdhere strictly to the following constraints:\n\n[PARAGRAPH META] is the LAW!!\n\nContextual Integration: The description of the previous paragraph is available in [PRIOR_RESULT]. Use this information to maintain continuity when relevant.\nCharacter & Action Precision: Focus on the specific actions mentioned in the #FOCUS PARAGRAPH while maintaining character traits and roles.\nAtmospheric Depth: Utilize the specified lighting (<meta.lighting>) and mood (<meta.mood>) to create depth. Describe textures, shadows, and environmental details that evoke the \"<meta.theme>\" theme without being overly explicit or gory.\n\nFormat: Output ONLY the contents of the [RESULT] block containing the scene description. Do not include conversational filler, explanations, or markdown headers.\n\nEnsure the output captures the specific narrative moment within the broader context of the story.\n\n"
      ]
    },
